title: No 'normals' on Twisted Treeline??
body:
Am I missing something? I wanted to queue up for a blind pick normals for Twisted Treeline only to find that there's only 3v3 Ranked Flex as the only option?
Is this just an OCE thing?

replies.body:
Twisted Treeline Normal Blind:

Friday: 3:00pm - 1:00am AEST

Twisted Treeline Ranked Flex:

Saturday: 3:00pm - 1:00am AEST
Sunday: 3:00pm - 1:00am AEST

https://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/announcements/wgM0WBsO-queue-schedule-updated-apr-3rd-2018

Blind pick for Twisted Treeline is available on Fridays from 3pm until 1am the following morning. Saturdays and Sundays have ranked for Twisted Treeline during the same period. 

Source: https://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/announcements/wgM0WBsO-queue-schedule-updated-apr-3rd-2018
